Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Kamala wants to spend $1.7 trillion dollars in wasteful spending, causing more inflation—and she says it’s “A MISTAKE” to ask her how she’s going to pay for it. Kamala Harris can’t answer how she’d pay for ANY of her new liberal spending schemes that will bankrupt our country.She has no clue how she’d pay for $25,000 to every first-time home buyer, including illegals. No clue how she’d pay for Free Healthcare for illegals. No clue how she’d pay for giving Social Security and Medicare to illegals. No clue how she’d pay for BILLIONS in Student Loan Giveaways. No clue how she’d pay for the $100 trillion dollar Green New Scam. And no clue how she’d pay for hundreds of billions of dollars in new Foreign Aid giveaways. That’s why it’s so important to VOTE TRUMP to stop the reckless spending. I will stop the special interest giveaways, cut waste, and restore COMMON SENSE.
